  "customHelp": "TCG Arena auto-routes cards by type using autoPlayFromHand, but only for single-type decks. Host: load FS Host Shared Setup Pack (All Shared)—cards will be drawn to hand, then manually place them to correct zones (Loot Deck, Treasure Deck, etc.) by type. Or use individual single-type decks (FS Shared Loot Deck, Treasure Deck, etc.) for automatic placement. Players: use FS Character Mulligan Deck (All)—characters auto-route to Character zone. Draw 1, mulligan once, then manually select matching item from FS Starting Items Pool (All).",
